race.comment: ADJOURNED (3) is a handy type who notched his 17th career success when too good (21.84) from Box 4 at this track. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Form reads well for this. FORGIVENESS (2) is worth forgiving for her last effort when fifth (16.86) at Q Straight over 300m. One of the main contenders. GOLDSTAR BRUISER (1) produced a moderate performance last time when eighth at this track over 457m behind Juniper Rose (26.75) in a Grade 5. Has ability and can measure up. HOPE'S ZONE (6) is always a threat when she races at this journey.
